job.title: OPSC Recruitment 2021- Apply Online for 92 Asst Soil Conservation Officer Vacancy
job.body:
Total Vacancies:139

Name of the post:

  • Post Graduate Teacher 

Description:

Odisha Public Service Commission  issued a total of 139 vacancies for the posts of Post Graduate Teacher  . The online application for these posts under OPSC shall start from 24-03-2021. The eligible and interested candidates can apply for this online application before 23-04-2021 For further detailed information regarding educational qualifications, age limit, selection procedure, how to apply, etc. for these posts is mentioned below. For more such updates do visit theprograd.com .The ProGrad jobs.

 

Mode of application & application fee:

The application fee for OPSC Recruitment 2021:

  • Mode of application: Online
  • The application fee for the SC, ST of Odisha, PwD is NIL
  • The application fee for OTHER is 500/-
  • For more details, you can refer to the notification. The link is given at the bottom.

Important dates:

  • The Starting date to apply online is 24-03-2021
  • The Last date to apply online is 23-04-2021

Educational qualification:

  • You must have a Master Degree/ M.Sc., B.Ed. to apply for the post of Post Graduate Teacher 

Age limit criteria:

  • The minimum age required to apply is: 21 Years
  • The maximum age required to apply is: 32 Years
  • For age relaxation criteria,you can refer to the notification. The link is given below in The ProGrad jobs.

Pay Scale:

  • The pay scale as per 7th pay commission for the post of Post Graduate Teacher is : Rs 56,800 per month
  • Check the detailed notification also something has missed.

Detailed vacancies:

The vacancies in detail are given below. Check below that OPSC issued this notification for which posts.

How to apply for OPSC Recruitment 2021?

  • First, visit the official website.
  • Register yourself on the portal of OPSC
  • Login yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification of Post Graduate Teacher .
  • Fill up the complete details that are asked in the application form.
  • Upload your photo and signature with the dimensions asked in the instructions.
  • Submit the application fee
  • Finally, download the application form for future needs.
